  "research_html": "<div class=\"research-section\">\n<p class=\"research-text\">Fragments on Divine Vision is a verse work attributed to Menophilus the Poet, reportedly consisting of sixteen passages. No corroborating evidence for the work, its author, or its attribution exists within the standard corpus of ancient Greek literature or scholarly reference works. The title suggests a poetic treatment of divine revelation or epiphany, a theme supported by the content of the extant fragments, which describe a profound, overwhelming visual experience that surpasses all earthly and even Olympian wonders. The narrator recounts a journey across Europe, Libya, and all of Asia, witnessing countless marvels, yet asserts that he never beheld such a radiance, a powerful and indescribable apparition that seized his mind. The experience is portrayed as physically and psychologically transformative, causing his limbs to dissolve and his past sufferings to fall away. The fragments culminate in a vision of a radiant figure, adorned with ever-blooming tresses, emerging from blessed waters and compared to the Graces. Despite this evocative content, the work&#x27;s manuscript tradition, the sources of the fragments, and their thematic coherence remain entirely undocumented. While the name Menophilus is attested for other historical and grammatical figures, no known source connects it to this poetic composition. Its complete absence from the historical record precludes any substantive assessment of its literary or philosophical significance.</p>\n</div>",
  "rows": [
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.1",
      "text": "[ln_1]Εὐρώπην Λιβύην",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.2",
      "text": "τε καὶ Ἀσίδα πᾶσαν ἀμείψας θαύμασα μυρία καλὰ πολυπλαν〈ί〉ης ὑπὸ λυγρῆς, ἀλλ’ οὔπω",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.3",
      "text": "τοιοῦτον ἴδον σέλας, οὐδ’ ἐν Ὀλύμπῳ αὐτοὺς ἀθανάτους 〈περ〉 ὀΐομαι ἶσον ἰδέσθαι,[ln_5]οἷον ἄελπτον ἄπιστον ἐμὸν νόον ἥρπασε φάσμα καρτερόν, οὔ τι",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.4",
      "text": "φατειόν· ὑπ’ ἀμφασίῃ δ’ ἀλεγεινῇ θυμὸς ἄδην",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.5",
      "text": "πεπότητο, λύθεν δέ μοι ἅψεα πάντα ἐκ κεφαλῆς εἰς ἴχνος, ἀπώλετο δ’ Ἑλλὰς ἅπασα ἐκ",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.6",
      "text": "στηθέων, καὶ πάντα",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.7",
      "text": "χαμαὶ πέσεν, ὅσσα",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.8",
      "text": "περ ἔτλην[ln_10]ὑγρῇ τε",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.9",
      "text": "τραφερῇ τε κυλινδόμενος",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.10",
      "text": "περὶ νόστον. τόσσον γὰρ",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.11",
      "text": "περὶ θυμὸν ἀπείριτον ἵκετο θάμβος. μέλψαι δὲ μνήσειας ἀειθαλέας",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.12",
      "text": "πλοκαμῖδας, οἵαις κυδιόωσαν ἀπ’ ὀλβίστων",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.13",
      "text": "σε λοετρῶν",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.14",
      "text": "φαιδρὴν εἶδον ἅπασαν ἐειδομένην",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.15",
      "text": "Χαρίτεσσιν[ln_15]ἐρχομέναις",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "text",
      "reference": "book 558.16",
      "text": "πρὸς Ὄλυμπον Ἀκιδαλίης ἀπὸ πηγῆς.",
      "witness_prefix": "",
      "speaker": null
    }
  ],
